item.title: Interests
item.description: So…somehow I’m writing this: the first post of the website. But…when will this find itself published and accessible to all? No idea. Part of what I’ve gone through in the process of thinking and building this website is a glimpse into something that I can fall prey to at times. When I was just thinking about this website and what this place could hold, then I was more or less overwhelmed.
